short.ar: حرك الثقب لجمع الكائنات البيضاء وإكمال الأقسام.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you ready to swallow cubes with a crazy hole! Swallow the cubes of the right color and start this fun adventure.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Hole Eating Cube Game Features
✓ Cartoon graphics
✓ 4+ Level
✓ Realistic vibrate
✓ Basic control

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Hole Eating Cube Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
